name: Hello Bluebird
comments: This track was released on Grey Gull 1398 under the name "Original Dixie Rag Pickers" and on Madison 1614 under the name "Newport Society Orchestra". "Newport Society Orchestra" is a name that was often used by Ben Selvin and His Orchestra, and several sides released under that name have been confirmed to have been recorded by Ben Selvin. "Hello Bluebird" is not one of those confirmed recordings. "Original Dixie Rag Pickers" was a name used for recordings by many artists when relased on Grey Gull. The editors have been unable to establish the real identity of the artist behind "Hello Bluebird".
